channel.title: [PI] EliteProdigyz V2
channel.description:
[size=18pt][font=impact]EliteProdigyz V2[/font][/size]
Why I released?
I was working on this project with Luckycharm he posts on he a bit. But, Then I wasn't proud of this so I think I'm going to start on another base. The base and client is Hybrid Pvp v3. Lots of releases have been on this lately, I'm gonna make this one stand out. All of the Hybrid Pvp v3 Servers I've seen on here had little change. Mine has Mid-Change you could say. The project is [size=36pt]50%[/size] done. I didn't get to start on the hard programming stuff. Features I added are below this and Enjoy! And again I'm basically being generous and giving this out to the public for new programmers!
Features I added.
Staffzone Hangout Skill Areas/Portals 20% Finished Donaterzone (Sorry I was lazy to finish :|) Tradezone. (Because of home is small.) Dragon Dungeon. Fixed some Npcs made them like Rs. Added fun pk! New Home! (Stable) Made the Eco not over-powered! Private Rooms UnderGround Altars. (No space at Home.) Bumped up the Exp rates for a stable server. Made Donaters not so over benefited. Custom Skill zones. New Jail. Added Tutorials in it for Beginner Programmers/Coders.
[size=24pt]Pictures[/size] Home map. I thought Rimmington would be a nice home since its different. [img]http://i54.tinypic.com/33utu15.png[/img] Staffzone. Portals lead to Private rooms! [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/20sd0uo.jpg[/img] Private room 2 (Guthix Portal) [img]http://i53.tinypic.com/mjlnk0.jpg[/img] Trade - This was made for trading so its not cramped at home. [img]http://i54.tinypic.com/k9uuyc.jpg[/img] Hangout - Just a place to hangout and talk its like a 2nd home to make home less cramped. [img]http://i51.tinypic.com/2v0gaw8.jpg[/img] Custom Home I made. (Credits to LuckyCharm for the Idea :D) [img]http://i55.tinypic.com/s245d1.jpg[/img] Dragon Dungeon - Boost Economy for Dragon bones and the need of Dragon bones.(It didn't have the dragons in it at this time because it was taken before I added Drags. [img]http://i54.tinypic.com/53tdow.jpg[/img] Fun PK - Don't lose anything yay [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/15o78l0.jpg[/img] Items that are on server (Torva Pernex Virtus Primal Chaotics Master Dung + Dung cape (t) ) [img]http://i52.tinypic.com/vq0575.jpg[/img] Tutorials/Spoon feeds all out the source/client to help you new programmers! [img]http://i53.tinypic.com/2ymbs7t.jpg[/img]
Okay I claim to have Edited this. I change basically everything in each little way. (I only left couple teleports alone.) Not everything but most.
Don't Troll, Don't flame. All I ask. Once again this project is 50% done. 100% will be V3 and it will be a whole other world.
Client download: http://up.ht/l5Ja9e (3.4 Mb) Source download: http://up.ht/j61ubE (9.5 Mb)
Credits: Omgitsshane Everyone who did Hybrid Pvp
DO NOT POST THIS ON RUNE SERVERR
[size=36pt]Note: If it doesn't work compile![/size]
